  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">• We show that periodic conditions mathematically lead to large-scale anisotropy in turbulent flows. • This anisotropy index can be about 10% of the mean values. • A decomposition method by employing spherical harmonics is proposed to remove this anisotropy.</subfield>
